{
  "stem": "13483.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 116.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, they were some of the Jewish families that were left behind there, who were also clean-- cleaning up the shul there, cleaning up the synagogue there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got to know these people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I spoke to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took them food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I've still got-- found some letters that they wrote to my wife, thanking me, you know, thanking us for supplying them with food.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, I still remember the address.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they lived at a place called 23 [INAUDIBLE], in Tilburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what his occupation was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think he might have been a merchant or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And his wife, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeta, ?] they didn't have any children at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know if they were hidden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I-- I was told that they managed to hide themselves in somewhere in Tilburg, with them and the other family, [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Pollack. ?] And I think after three days we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they communicated with me, following up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They wrote letters to me whilst I was still in Holland, or whilst I was still in the forces.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they did write a couple of letters to my wife here in London.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think there was a few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were the only two families I remember, or--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or who I communicated with.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- yet-- oh, incidentally, they-- William Esse, a man, actually gave me his yellow Star of David, which I donated to the Jewish museum here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No, I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they just said, they'd managed to sort of keep away from the Germans, who were occupied in Tilburg at the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, of course they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, most of the Dutch people were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
